<h2><a href="http://www.publicintegrity.org/2015/02/12/16748/us-court-orders-hsbc-usa-provide-details-customers-offshore-law-firm" title="U.S. court orders HSBC USA to provide details of customers with offshore law firm">U.S. court orders HSBC USA to provide details of customers with offshore law firm</a></h2>
<div class="field field-name-field-authors field-type-relation field-label-hidden">
    
  <h4 class="authors">By <span><span class="author"><a href="http://www.publicintegrity.org/authors/charles-r-babcock" title="Charles R. Babcock">Charles R. Babcock</a></span></span></h4>  <h4 class="pubdate"><time datetime="2015-02-12T11:02:23-05:00">February 12, 2015</time></h4>
  <div class="field-items">
      </div>
</div>


</hgroup>
</header>
<div class="main-body"></div>
</div>
</section></div></aside><aside class="relation packaged"><div class="relation-inner grid_4 suffix_desktop-large_3 suffix_desktop_1 stacked float-right" data-sigil="relation"><section>
<div id="node-16753" class="node node-article teaser-view title-author-1x1-1col clearfix">
<div class="divider"></div>
<header>
<hgroup>
<div class="field field-name-field-mini-image field-type-relation field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even"><div class="item even"><div id="node-16739" class="node node-image title-1x1-1col clearfix"><div class="divider"></div><div class="field field-name-field-image-file field-type-image field-label-hidden">
  <div class="field-items">
		<div class="field-item"><a href="http://www.publicintegrity.org/2015/02/12/16753/vote-lynch-delayed-wake-hsbc-revelations"><picture itemprop="image" data-alt="" data-default-src="http://cloudfront-5.publicintegrity.org/files/styles/1x1-1col/public/img/loretta-lynch.jpg?itok=tG1kXd6_"><source srcset="http://cloudfront-3.publicintegrity.org/files/styles/1x1-1col/public/img/loretta-lynch.jpg?itok=tG1kXd6_, http://cloudfront-4.publicintegrity.org/files/styles/1x1-2col/public/img/loretta-lynch.jpg?itok=GwzGu_k2 2x" /><img width="100%" src="" srcset="" alt=""/></picture></a></div>
	</div>
